==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intrenchant
<hw>In*trench"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>trenchant</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not to be gashed
or marked with furrows.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As easy mayest thou the <qex>intrenchant</qex> air⟦br⟧
With thy keen sword impress, as make me bleed.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intrenchment</ent>⟦br⟧
